thread.title: Ingenico Group expects to achieve another double digit increase in sales in US next year
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Ingenico Group expects to achieve another double digit increase in sales in US next year | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Ingenico Group expects to achieve another double digit increase in sales in US next year
text:
Sept 9 Ingenico Group SA :
* Ingenico Group takes strong lead on EMV in the US
* Anticipates sustained demand in all vertical markets and expects to achieve another double digit increase in sales in US next year
Source text for Eikon: (Gdynia Newsroom)
